title: Bug 6322 - All types dialog shows obfuscated classes
description: Bug 6322 - All types dialog shows obfuscated classes. In JDK 1.4, the dialog includes obfuscated classes (a, a1, b, c, d) etc.
OB: The All types dialog is displaying obfuscated classes prominently.
EB: The obfuscated classes should be displayed with less prominence in the All types dialog.
SR: Update the All types dialog to display obfuscated classes with reduced prominence.
